1、download docker


Link：https://desktop.docker.com/mac/m1preview/Docker-AppleSilicon-Preview7.dmg

2、install

3、setting

Open docker desktop

Add code below

"registry-mirrors": [
    "https://dockerhub.azk8s.cn",
    "https://hub-mirror.c.163.com",
    "https://mirror.baidubce.com"
  ],

4、testing

Open terminal, input

docker run -d -p 80:80 docker/getting-started


normal use.
